            <title>[SOLR-1450] DIH - Jdbc connection properties such as batchSize are not applied if the driver jar is placed in solr_home/lib</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1450</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When JDBC driver is placed in &amp;lt;solr-home&amp;gt;/lib (as instructed by DIHQuickStart page of Solr wiki), but not in tomcat&apos;s lib directory, the JDBC connection will not be configured as specified in the DIH configuration.  Attributes like autoCommit, readOnly and batchSize will be ignored.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Generic&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
